# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok over ### bluetongue cases have been detected in <unk> province of central france recently , the provincial council said in a statement wednesday .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (c / council
            :mod (p / province))
      :ARG1 (d / detect-01
            :ARG1 (c2 / case-04
                  :ARG1 (b / bluetongue))
            :time (r / recent)
            :location (p2 / province
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Central"
                        :op2 "France")))
      :medium (s2 / statement
            :time (w / wednesday)))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok two weeks after its launching , the russian-built module designed to house future residents of the u.s.-led international space station is ready to link up with the other components of the slowly developing orbital outpost .
# ::alignments
(r / ready-02
      :ARG1 (m / module
            :ARG1-of (b / build-01
                  :ARG0 (c / country
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Russia")))
            :ARG1-of (d / design-01
                  :ARG3 (h / house-01
                        :ARG0 m
                        :ARG1 (p / person
                              :ARG0-of (r2 / reside-01
                                    :ARG1 (s / station
                                          :mod (ii / international)
                                          :ARG1-of (l / lead-02
                                                :ARG0 (c2 / country
                                                      :name (n2 / name
                                                            :op1 "U.S."))))
                                    :time (f / future))))))
      :ARG2 (l2 / link-up-02
            :ARG1 m
            :ARG2 (c3 / component
                  :mod (o / other)
                  :part-of (o2 / outpost
                        :ARG0-of (o3 / orbit-01)
                        :ARG1-of (d2 / develop-01
                              :ARG1-of (s2 / slow-05)))))
      :time (a / after
            :op1 (l3 / launch-01
                  :ARG1 m)
            :quant (t / temporal-quantity
                  :quant 2
                  :unit (w / week))))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok second-seeded patty schnyder of switzerland defeated austrian teenager tamira paszek #-# #-# sunday to win the bali open , her first title for three years .
# ::alignments
(d / defeat-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Patty"
                  :op2 "Schnyder")
            :ARG1-of (s / seed-01
                  :ARG2 (c / country
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Switzerland"))
                  :ord (o / ordinal-entity
                        :value 2)))
      :ARG1 (p2 / person
            :name (n3 / name
                  :op1 "Tamira"
                  :op2 "Paszek")
            :mod (t / teenager)
            :mod (c2 / country
                  :name (n4 / name
                        :op1 "Australia")))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (s2 / sunday))
      :purpose (w / win-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (g / game
                  :name (n5 / name
                        :op1 "Bali"
                        :op2 "Open")
                  :ARG2-of (t2 / title-01
                        :ARG1 p2
                        :ord (o2 / ordinal-entity
                              :value 1
                              :range (t3 / temporal-quantity
                                    :quant 3
                                    :unit (y / year)))))))

                  :ARG1 (s2 / society
                        :mod (c / country

                                    :op1 "Spain")))
                  :duration (n4 / nearly
                        :op1 (t2 / temporal-quantity
                              :quant 1
                              :unit (y / year)))))
      :ARG1 (c2 / cease-01
            :ARG1 (f / fire-01)
            :mod (p2 / permanent))
      :time (w2 / wednesday)
      :op2 (s3 / say-01
            :ARG0 g
            :ARG1 (t3 / turn-01
                  :ARG0 g
                  :ARG1 (a3 / attend-02
                        :ARG0 g
                        :ARG1 (a4 / achieve-01

                                          :ARG1 (p3 / politics))))))))

            :ARG1 (s2 / stay-01

                              :ARG2 (e2 / epidemic
                                    :mod (g / globe)))))))
